attributes.description: TYCHON captures the status of Trellix, Elastic Defender, and Windows Defender features and versions on endpoints and reports the information in this dashboard.

params.markdown:
### Endpoint Protection Status
TYCHON tracks specific Endpoint Protection vendors for enabled features, installed software, and definition versions. Currently, TYCHON supports Trellix, Elastic Defender, and Windows Defender.

filter.query: tychon.windows_defender.service.antimalware.status : "Disabled" or tychon.windows_defender.service.antispyware.status :"Disabled" or tychon.windows_defender.service.antivirus.status : "Disabled" or tychon.windows_defender.service.behavior_monitor.status : "Disabled"  or tychon.windows_defender.service.ioav_protection.status : "Disabled" or tychon.windows_defender.service.nis.status : "Disabled"  or tychon.windows_defender.service.on_access_protection.status : "Disabled"  or tychon.windows_defender.service.real_time_protection.status : "Disabled"
not tychon.trellix.service.ens.version : "" or not tychon.trellix.service.accm.version :"" or not tychon.trellix.service.dlp.version :"" or not tychon.trellix.service.pa.version : ""
not tychon.elastic.service.endpoint.behavior_protection : "" and not tychon.elastic.service.endpoint.malware : "" and not tychon.elastic.service.endpoint.memory_protection : ""
